1
00:00:01,000 --> 00:00:04,000
你好，欢迎观看这个视频。
Hello, welcome to this video.

2
00:00:05,000 --> 00:00:08,500
今天我们来学习如何使用实时字幕功能。
Today we will learn how to use the real-time subtitle feature.

3
00:00:10,000 --> 00:00:13,000
首先，导入一个视频文件。
First, import a video file.

4
00:00:14,500 --> 00:00:18,000
然后，点击标记开始按钮记录起始时间。
Then, click the mark start button to record the start time.

5
00:00:19,000 --> 00:00:22,000
观看视频内容，结束时点击标记结束。
Watch the video content, and click mark end when finished.

6
00:00:23,500 --> 00:00:27,000
添加字幕后，可以点击翻译按钮。
After adding subtitles, you can click the translate button.

7
00:00:28,000 --> 00:00:31,500
系统会优先使用记忆库和语料库。
The system will prioritize using the memory and corpus.

8
00:00:33,000 --> 00:00:36,500
如果没有匹配，会自动调用翻译API。
If there is no match, it will automatically call the translation API.

9
00:00:38,000 --> 00:00:41,000
翻译完成后，可以自定义字幕样式。
After translation, you can customize the subtitle style.

10
00:00:42,500 --> 00:00:46,000
调整字幕位置、大小、颜色等参数。
Adjust subtitle position, size, color and other parameters.

11
00:00:47,000 --> 00:00:50,500
最后，导出为SRT文件保存。
Finally, export as an SRT file to save.

12
00:00:52,000 --> 00:00:55,000
感谢观看，祝你使用愉快！
Thanks for watching, hope you enjoy using it!
